79603.「ただいまより 第２回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加する:
Now it's time to introduce you to the lethal
beauties who will be participating in the 2nd
Annual Astrutia Queen Contest!

79604.「オーグリード大陸に咲く 一輪の赤いバラ！\n 前大会を 圧倒的な大差で制した:
A single red rose blooming in Ogreed Continent! The winner of the last tournament by an overwhelming margin, will he win again
this time?

79605.「第１回 アストルティア・クイーン！\n 向かうところ敵なしの\n オーガニック:
The 1st Astartia Queen! Organic beauty on her
way! Maille!

79606.「また このイベントに参加できて 光栄だわ。\n 今回も強敵ばかりだけど これは:
I'm honored to be back at this event. We have strong opponents again, but this is a serious competition... and I will defend my title as
queen!

79607.「風の町アズランに ひっそりと咲く 月見草！\n 前回 惜しくも優勝を逃した可憐:
The moonflowers, blooming quietly in Wind Town Azlan! The dainty girl who narrowly missed out on the championship last time is on fire for
Setsujok!

79608.「第１回 クイーン・コンテスト 第２位！\n 夢見る風乗り少女 フウラ！:
1st Queen Contest, 2nd Place! Dreaming Girl
Fuura!

79609.「わ…私 ケキちゃんと一緒じゃなくても\n 眠れるようになったし オトナになった:
I can sleep without Keki, and I've become an
adult. So I won't lose to you, Maille.

79610.「フランクな口調が チャームポイント！\n その明るさで みんなの心を わしづか:
His frank and friendly tone is his charm! The man whose cheerful personality has captured everyone's hearts has joined us again from
heaven!

79611.「第１回 クイーン・コンテスト 第３位！\n 天然☆予知っ娘ママ アルウェ王妃ち:
The 1st Queen Contest, 3rd Place! Natural Mama
Queen Alwe, the foresighted mama!

79612.「は～い。ミローレさん よくできたわねー。\n よばれて とびでた アルウェです:
Ha~yes. Milore, you did a great job! I was
called by you, and I was Alwe.

79613.「あたしぃ 予知っ娘だから 今回も\n 結果は見えてるのぉ。う～んと 今回はねぇ:
I'm the girl with the foresight, so I know the
outcome this time too. Well, this time,
well...nothing!

79614.「ジュレットの町に舞い降りた 心優しき天使！\n その見た目に反して いかなる逆:
A kind-hearted angel who landed in Julet!
Despite her appearance, she has a heart of
gold that can overcome any adversity...

79617.「私を 選んでくれる人たちがいる……。\n その人の想いを裏切らないよう 前に進:
There are people who choose me... and I want to move forward so that I don't betray their wishes! If this is how I am, please support
me!

79618.「岳都ガタラを駆け抜ける 黒い影！\n 今度こそは あなたのハートを盗んでみせる:
A black shadow runs through Mount Gatara!
This time I will steal your heart! I know the
heavens! Earth knows! Only men know...

79619.「美少女怪盗ポイックリン！\n 華麗に 参上でございますわっ！:
Phantom Thief Poiclin! Here she comes in all
her finery!

79620.「私に盗めぬ物は なし！ 今回はバッチリ\n クイーンの座を 盗んでみせますわ！:
There's nothing I can't steal! This time, I
will steal the queen's throne! All you
Dwarves!

79621.「あこがれの いやし系お姉様！\n ああ！ そのムネに抱かれて 眠りたい……！\:
I've always wanted to be your pampered sister!
Ah! I want to sleep in her arms...! Last time,
you did a great job!

79623.「まさかの大健闘だって！？ 失礼だね！\n あたしゃ いつも 勝つ気で勝負してる:
I didn't expect you to do so well! That's
rude! I'm always trying to win! I'm just upset
about the lousy result last time!

79624.「この際 トシが 他よりいってるのは認めるよ！\n でも 女にとって重要なのは中:
I'll admit that Toshi is better than most! But
what's important for a woman is what's inside!
Okay? Think about who you choose!

79625.「さて ここまでが 前大会の出場者……。\n ここからは ニューフェイスの登場と:
Now, here are the contestants from the
previous tournament... from this point on, we
will be introducing new faces.

79626.「メルサンディ村の皆さん 見てますか？\n 金色の蝶が 大舞台に羽ばたきます。\:
Are you watching, Melsandy Village? A golden
butterfly flutters onto the stage. A simple
but graceful, authentic beauty...

79628.「このような大舞台……私には おそれ多いけど\n 村のみんなのためにも がんばり:
I am afraid of this big stage, but I will do my best for the sake of everyone in the village. If it is all right with me, I would
appreciate your support.

79629.「セレドの町に君臨する 絶対的女王様！\n その絶対的カリスマに 国民たちも絶対:
The absolute queen of the Town of Celed! Her charisma is so charismatic that the people of Ceredo absolutely submit to her! But she also
has a gentle side to her.

79631.「ふん……。あの ミローレっていう人\n 大人にしては まあまあの紹介をするじゃ:
Well... that Milore person gives an okay
introduction for an adult. The "rebellious"
part is a bit superfluous, though.

79632.「そこの あなた！ 私に尽くしてみない？\n 私をクイーンにしてくれたら おやつ:
Hey, you! Why don't you do me a favor? I'll
give you lots of treats if you make me your
queen. I'll give you lots of treats.

79633.「みんなを ぐいぐい引っ張る行動力と\n 魔物をいたわる優しい心を あわせ持つ\:
She is a super hybrid girl who has both the
energy to lead others and the kind heart to
care for monsters...

79634.「アラハギーロ王国の青き反逆者 セラフィ！:
Seraphi, the Blue Rebel of the Kingdom of
Al-Ahagiro!

79635.「えへへ。クイーンになったら 人間も魔物も\n なかよく暮らせる そんな国を作り:
Hehehe. When I become queen, I want to create a country where humans and monsters can live together in harmony. Everyone... I'm counting
on your support.

79636.「まもの使いハウスの うるわしき聖母！\n やさしいママさんの魅力に 男性陣はメ:
Our Lady of Leap of Faith at Monster Master House! The men are smitten by the charms of this gentle mama! But don't be too nice to
her!

79638.「ファーベル 見てるー？\n お母さん 出たわよー！: Fabel, are you seeing this? Mom, it's out!

79639.「クイーンになって お家に帰るからねー！\n おばあちゃんの言うこと ちゃんと聞:
I'm going home a queen! You just listen to
your grandma and stay a little while longer!

79640.「以上 １０名の美女たちが\n クイーンの座をかけて コンテストを争います。:
These 10 beauties will compete for the title
of queen.

79641.「果たして 栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will be crowned with glory? It's up to you
to decide!

79642.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n 今回も選りすぐりの美女が そろいました。\n:
What do you think of ? We have a great selection of beautiful women for you to choose from this time. Did you find your
favorite one?

79643.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n その方のチョコ作りを 手伝っ:
If you decide on a beautiful woman who you
think would make a good queen, please help her
make the chocolates.

79644.「あなたが チョコ作りを手伝った相手に\n あなたの１票が 投じられるのです。\:
Your vote will go to the person you helped
make the chocolates. Please think carefully
before you make your choice.

79645.「選び終わりましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
When you have finished your selection, please
stop by my place for a chat. I'll be outside.

79646.「ただいまより 第２回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発表:
We will now announce the results of the 2nd
Astor Tia Queen Contest!

79647.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who is worthy of being crowned Queen of our
Chocolat Fontenay Castle?! The results are
in!!

79648.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！: Ladies and gentlemen! Attention on stage!
